      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i feel like i can manage it with some ibuprofen and icing it. i've had sprains before and they were fine with just rest. if i just stay off it for like 3 or 4 days and keep it iced, isnt that basically the same thing as getting an x-ray? it just seems like a lot of trouble for a possible sprain.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
